<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">locale</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The locale code. (en, ko, en_US, ko_KR.utf8, etc. <ref refid="classDali_1_1TextAbstraction_1_1ICU" kindref="compound">ICU</ref> accepts most formats of locale code), The usual expected form is language_locale (ko_KR). </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
